They've helped me out, and I've helped them out.

538
00:28:13,942 --> 00:28:15,222
现在我想他们会帮你的。
Now I think they'll help you out.

539
00:28:15,903 --> 00:28:18,882
就连保罗和我也抽出时间来这里观鸟。
Even Paul and I have found some time to do a little birding here.

540
00:28:18,906 --> 00:28:19,907
我们是狂热的观鸟者。
We're avid birders.

541
00:28:19,990 --> 00:28:21,050
是的。这真的是一种精妙的爱好。
Yes. It's an exquisite hobby, really.

542
00:28:21,074 --> 00:28:22,075
是的。
Yes.

543
