These are extinct.

546
00:28:28,790 --> 00:28:30,375
是的，我们有后两种。
Yes, we have the last two.

547
00:28:31,084 --> 00:28:32,628
尼克巴，鸽子。
The Nicobar, uh, pigeon.

548
00:28:32,711 --> 00:28:33,712
是的。
Yes.

549
00:28:33,795 --> 00:28:35,505
他们一度还活着。
They were alive at one point.

550
00:28:35,589 --> 00:28:37,466
这是北美野鸡。
And this is the North American pheasant.

551
00:28:37,549 --> 00:28:41,386
这是一只北美野鸡，我喜欢称它为野鸡中的农民。
It's a North American pheasant, which I like to call the peasant of pheasants.

552
00:28:41,470 --> 00:28:42,930
你看，它们太常见了。
They're so common, you see.

553
00:28:43,013 --> 00:28:44,848
-但是它们很漂亮。——是的。
- But they are beautiful. - Yes.

554
00:28:44,932 --> 00:28:46,642
它的羽毛真漂亮。
The plumage is really outstanding.

555
00:28:46,725 --> 00:28:54,066
所以，你知道，我们很乐意为你的脸付钱，不管你需要什么整容治疗，嗯……顶级的，最好的。
So, you know, we're happy to pay for the faces, whatever cosmetic healing you might need, uh... Top-shelf, nothing but the best.

556
00:28:54,149 --> 00:29:00,113
是的,是的。还有阿姆斯特丹的美好生活，在经历了这一切之后你应该在这里休息和自由。
Yes, yes. As well as a good life here in Amsterdam, where you deserve a rest and some freedom after what you've been through.

557
00:29:01,073 --> 00:29:05,619
将来我们需要你们这些好人帮忙的时候，我们会来找你们的。
We'll come a-calling sometime in the future when we need you good people to help us out.

558
00:29:05,702 --> 00:29:06,703
是的。
Yes.

559
00:29:06,787 --> 00:29:14,670
因为总有一天我们会对这些制造这场我们无法理解的战争的疯子说“够了”。
Because there will come a time to say "enough" to these madmen who create this war we cannot make any sense of.

560
00:29:14,753 --> 00:29:17,172
这怪物怎么可能再出现呢?
Well, how could this monstrosity repeat itself?

561
00:29:17,255 --> 00:29:19,424
这应该是一场结束所有战争的战争。
It's supposed to be the war to end all wars.

562
00:29:19,508 --> 00:29:20,509
正确的。
Right.

563
00:29:20,592 --> 00:29:23,762
因为梦会重复，因为它会忘记自己。
Because the dream repeats itself since it forgets itself.

564
00:29:23,845 --> 00:29:26,014
这就是为什么它会重复。
That's why it repeats itself.

565
00:29:26,765 --> 00:29:27,766
这是好的部分。
This is the good part.

566
00:29:27,849 --> 00:29:29,935
但不好的部分总有一天会再次出现。
But the bad part will come again one day.

567
00:29:30,018 --> 00:29:33,981
但现在，这是阿姆斯特丹的好地方。
But for now, this is the good part, in Amsterdam.

568
00:29:37,901 --> 00:29:39,128
这些是灯。
These are the lights right here.

569
00:29:39,152 --> 00:29:40,213
它们可能有点棘手。
They can be a little tricky.

570
00:29:40,237 --> 00:29:42,739
