00:32:51,052 --> 00:32:52,304
你可以选择你的朋友。
You can choose your friends.

621
00:32:52,387 --> 00:32:53,972
你不能选择你的家庭。
You can't choose your family.

622
00:32:54,848 --> 00:33:01,229
我选择了你。这……我有点尴尬了，因为你可能不这么想。
And I choose you. And this... I'm getting embarrassed, because you might not feel the same way.

623
00:33:01,313 --> 00:33:06,860
但这段感情，可能是我生命中最重要的东西。
But this relationship, probably the most important thing in my life.

624
00:33:07,986 --> 00:33:10,030
是的。
Yeah.

625
00:33:10,113 --> 00:33:11,615
我们同意。所以保持。
We do agree. So stay.

626
00:33:11,990 --> 00:33:13,658
但我不能放弃碧翠丝。
But I can't quit Beatrice.

627
00:33:15,327 --> 00:33:16,328
我爱她。
I love her.

628
00:33:17,412 --> 00:33:19,664
当然，他们说你会有奖章。
Sure, they say you'll have medals.

629
00:33:20,081 --> 00:33:22,209
你会和公园大道很合得来的。
You'll fit in on Park Avenue.

630
00:33:23,126 --> 00:33:26,296
这就是我受到的英雄般的欢迎。
Well, this was the hero's welcome I received.

631
00:33:26,379 --> 00:33:29,299
