You are blacklisted.

638
00:33:43,021 --> 00:33:44,981
走了。离开。你必须离开。你必须离开这里。
Go. Leave. You must leave. You must leave here.

639
00:33:45,774 --> 00:33:48,068
不要去公寓。我将……我会给你寄衣服的。
Don't go to the apartment. I'll... I'll send you clothes.

640
00:33:48,151 --> 00:33:51,196
伯特伦,呆!我很抱歉。
Bertram, stay! I'm sorry.

